    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Creation of images by hyperspectral remote sensors which collect data simultaneously in dozens or hundreds of narrow, adjacent spectral bands. The images thus created are more detailed than those of other multispectral sensors with just a few relatively broad wavelength bands.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
